🔷 Semantic Versioning (SemVer)

Format:

```text
MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH
```

Example:

```text
1.2.3
```

Meaning:

* MAJOR → Breaking changes
* MINOR → New features
* PATCH → Bug fixes

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 Version Symbols

| Symbol | Meaning            |
| ------ | ------------------ |
| ^      | Compatible version |
| ~      | Minor updates      |
| *      | Any version        |

---

🔷 NPM vs NPX

| npm              | npx          |
| ---------------- | ------------ |
| Installs package | Runs package |
| Permanent        | Temporary    |

Example:

```bash
npx create-react-app my-app
```

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 Environment Variables

Use `.env` file:

```text
PORT=3000
API_KEY=12345
```

Install dotenv:

```bash
npm install dotenv
```

Use:

```javascript
require("dotenv").config();
console.log(process.env.PORT);
```
